{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"26":"Chapters on Sacrifices"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3161,"arabicnumber":3161,"text":"২/৩১৬১। ইবনে উমার (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম ঈদের মাঠে কোরবানীর পশু যবেহ করতেন।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan Or Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":26,"hadith":42}}]}